0% increase from a year earlier. Ye, 45, would earn $147 million in royalti=
es from those sales, and the preliminary analysis found that the value of f=
uture footwear royalties could range from $1.75 billion to $3 billion.=C2=
=A0

A few weeks=C2=A0ago he had $122 million in the bank and was a billionaire;=
 today he has $122 million in the bank and is not.

